      "props": {
        "text": "Sunday Apr 26 logged SKILL_LEADERBOARD_INSUFFICIENT_DATA — the skill only scanned aaronjmars/MiroShark (107 active forks, 0 with aeon.yml since it's an application repo). The actual aeon instance miroshark-aeon sat at list position 2 and never got read. Next Sunday (May 3) would have hit the same wall.",
